snippet.title: Last Wings - Feature Overview | PS4, PSVita & Xbox One
snippet.description:
Checkout our last gameplay trailer of Last Wings game.
Featuring a lot of combat scenes including multiplayer and split-screen.
Available on Q2/2016 for PS4, PSVita and Xbox One.
